item.description:
nuqneH is a truncated form of nuq DaneH, meaning &ldquo;What do you want?&rdquo;
It is a common misconception that this is &ldquo;the Klingon word for hello&rdquo;. In fact, Klingons have no word for hello. If a Klingon wishes to say something, they'll walk up to you and say it, without wasting time - as they see it - on idle chatter.
nuqjatlh? is a truncated form of nuq Dajatlh?, meaning &ldquo;What did you say?
